       "functools.update_wrapper.__annotations__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('dict') == True — update_wrapper is a pure-Python function in Lib/functools.py that assigns selected attributes from the wrapped function to the wrapper; it is defined with no type annotations so its __annotations__ dict is empty; __class__.__name__ for a dict is 'dict' (4 chars); str.__eq__('dict') returns True; no prior functools spec checks update_wrapper.__annotations__.__class__.__name__ via functoolsann77; new to extra77"]
